      "question_type": "multiple_choice_question",
      "question_text": "<p>A button should call <code>saveProfile</code> only when the user clicks it. The current code runs <code>saveProfile</code> immediately during page load:</p><pre><code>button.addEventListener('click', saveProfile())</code></pre><p>Which change fixes the problem?</p>",
